name: Evolve NASDAQ Technology Index Fund
longDescription: In order to achieve its investment objective and to obtain direct or indirect exposure to the Constituent Securities of the Index, the Evolve ETF may hold the Constituent Securities of the Index in approximately the same proportion as they are reflected in the Index or may hold securities of one or more exchange traded funds that replicate the performance of the Index, or a subset of such Index. The fund QQQT seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the NASDAQ1 Technology Sector Adjusted MarketCap Weighted Index, or any successor thereto.
